Subject: [PATCHv6 03/30] x86/tdx: Add __tdx_module_call() and __tdx_hypercall() helper functions
Date:   Wed, 16 Mar 2022 05:08:29 +0300
Message-Id: <20220316020856.24435-4-kirill.shutemov@linux.intel.com>
